g&ouml;r&auml; prostatany&#328; ululygy g&ouml;z &ouml;&#328;&uuml;nde
tutul&yacute;ar.&nbsp;PSA-ny kesgitlemek, &ccedil;i&#351; prosesini
ge&ccedil;irmek we bejergiden so&#328; n&auml;saglara g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik
etmek &uuml;&ccedil;in hem maslahat beril&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&Uuml;&ccedil; gezek prostat massaageyndan so&#328; alnan
pe&#351;ewd&auml;ki&nbsp;<b>PCA3 (Prostat Cancer Antigen 3)&nbsp;</b>markerini&nbsp;kesgitlemek,
prostata biopsi&yacute;asyny talap ed&yacute;&auml;n hassalary has gowy
sa&yacute;lamaga m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik ber&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;PCA3
ba&#351;langy&ccedil; &yacute;a-da ga&yacute;talan&yacute;an biopsi&yacute;any &yacute;erine
&yacute;etirmek &yacute;a-da ga&yacute;talamak &uuml;&ccedil;in PSA we
be&yacute;leki kliniki bellikler bilen bilelikde ulanylyp bilner.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

