ulgamyna &yacute;oka&#351;ma go&#351;ulanda bellenil&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;<i>Gormon
bejergisi&nbsp;</i>&ccedil;yl&#351;yrymly prostat m&auml;zini&#328;
&yacute;a&yacute;ramagy &uuml;&ccedil;in&nbsp;<i>g&ouml;rkezil&yacute;&auml;r&nbsp;</i>.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

