"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>, prostata m&auml;zini bejermek
&uuml;&ccedil;in radiasi&yacute;any maksatly ulanmakdyr.&nbsp;Radiasi&yacute;a
&yacute;&ouml;rite enjamlary&#328; k&ouml;megi bilen
d&ouml;redil&yacute;&auml;r &yacute;a-da radioaktiw maddalary&#328;
&ccedil;&uuml;&yacute;remeginden d&ouml;re&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Bu
&yacute;agda&yacute;da, &ccedil;i&#351; &ouml;&yacute;j&uuml;klerini&#328;
&ouml;l&uuml;mi &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;yk&yacute;ar, bu keseli&#328;
&ouml;smegini togtad&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Radiasi&yacute;a, n&auml;sag
&ouml;&yacute;j&uuml;kleri &ouml;ld&uuml;rmek, &yacute;ana&#351;yk adaty
dokumalara hem zeper &yacute;etirip biler, bu bolsa &yacute;aramaz
t&auml;sirleri&#328; &ouml;smegine getir&yacute;&auml;r, &yacute;&ouml;ne
&yacute;aramaz t&auml;sirleri&#328; t&ouml;wekgel&ccedil;iligi zy&yacute;anly
keseli&#328; netijelerinden has az.&nbsp;</span></p>

